title: Mystery surrounding brutal twin-murders of woman on date with hockey pro
itunes:title: Mystery surrounding brutal twin-murders of woman on date with hockey pro
description:
Who killed Darren Partch, and Wendi MIller -- a former hockey pro and a woman who advocates for children in family court?

The investigation led to a man who was already behind bars for a California crime spree.

Nancy's Expert Panel Weighs In:

Vincent Hill: Private Investigator

Dr. Bethany Marshall: Psychoanalyst

Kathleen Murphy: Family attorney

Dr. William Morrone: Medical Examiner

Robyn Walenski: Crime online investigative Reporter
